        port - Port for creating new object.
        timeout - Timeout for AVI Session.
        sessionID - The session ID.
        csrftoken - Csrftoken.
        token - Token for REST call if have.
        verify - For check SSL is want.
        retryConxnErrors - Retry connection timeout.
